  <div class="mb-4 px-4 pt-10">
    <h1 class="text-primary">About Me 👋</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="text-content px-4">
    <ul>
      <li>
        🏷️ I'm a full-stack developer who has worked with Astro.js, PHP and
        WordPress support.
      </li>
      <li>
        💻 Currently exploring Astro.js and React to build efficient,
        user-friendly solutions.
      </li>
      <li>
        🎯 Eager to learn more about software architecture, design patterns, and
        best practices.
      </li>
      <li>
        🏗️ Working on personal projects to sharpen my web development skills.
      </li>
      <li>🤝 Open to collaborating on open-source or web-focused projects.</li>
      <li>
        🔍 Ask me about technical support, web hosting, and how I apply that
        background to dev work.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>

